keyFacts: The document is a property record search for a Manhattan parcel, showing a history of financial and legal transactions.
A mortgage for $9,045,000 and a deed for $15,075,000 were recorded on the same day in April 2016.
The property has a recorded history dating back to at least 1994, with various deeds, agreements, and a power of attorney.
The document reference 'EFTA00151367' and 'EFTA00151368' suggests it is part of the Epstein-related document release.
